        "content": "### ⚠️ RADIUS Prometheus metrics are not yet implemented\n\nThe panels below will remain empty until `aaa-radius-server` emits Prometheus metrics.\nSee **plan-08-radius-server.md § Observability** for the planned metric names.\n\n**Planned metrics:** `radius_requests_total{result, stage}` · `radius_request_duration_ms` · `radius_upstream_errors_total{upstream, status_code}`\n\nUntil then, monitor RADIUS activity via structured logs (`spdlog` JSON lines from the container) parsed in your SIEM."
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] }
